{"tid":2111132,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣漢光演習直升機墜毀 兩名官兵送院不治","createTime":"2020-07-16T10:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T11:40:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"946a6e875ea128b7a042fc73136662f85dc7394e","tid":2111132,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:36:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538138-20200716.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538138-20200716.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=435755c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538138-20200716.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=269b1c98\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538138-20200716.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n在台灣，一架參與漢光演習的直升機墜毀，兩名官兵送院不治。<br />\n<br />\n軍方指，涉事的OH-58D戰搜直升機，執行漢光演習操演後，大約下午3時30分，返回新竹空軍基地時硬著陸及起火，兩名官兵送院搶救，其後不治。航空特戰指揮部已成立專案小組，調查事故原因，並要求各類直升機暫停任務派遣。台灣傳媒報道，同機型直升機已在兩年內，第三度發生意外。"},{"pid":"f400ff10bcb060ac8317f00b15f369909ebe0847","tid":2111132,"uid":30274,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:38:06.000Z","msg":"台灣D軍隊硬係比人一種業餘既感覺...."},{"pid":"37c6754ac473ba8199dea03741d0d52aa3750c3f","tid":2111132,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"946a6e875ea128b7a042fc73136662f85dc7394e","tid":2111132,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:36:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538138-20200716.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538138-20200716.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=435755c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538138-20200716.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=269b1c98\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538138-20200716.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n在台灣，一架參與漢光演習的直升機墜毀，兩名官兵送院不治。<br />\n<br />\n軍方指，涉事的OH-58D戰搜直升機，執行漢光演習操演後，大約下午3時30分，返回新竹空軍基地時硬著陸及起火，兩名官兵送院搶救，其後不治。航空特戰指揮部已成立專案小組，調查事故原因，並要求各類直升機暫停任務派遣。台灣傳媒報道，同機型直升機已在兩年內，第三度發生意外。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:47:23.000Z","msg":"OH-58D「奇奧瓦戰士」戰搜直升機，是我國在1991年8月「陸鵬專案」軍購的項目之一<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3230626\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3230626&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=0f5c3ef3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3230626&h=c0d49e76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3230626</a>"},{"pid":"c7ee0ee87085b2d272d261ca48b187be20b2c53d","tid":2111132,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f400ff10bcb060ac8317f00b15f369909ebe0847","tid":2111132,"uid":30274,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:38:06.000Z","msg":"台灣D軍隊硬係比人一種業餘既感覺...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:48:58.000Z","msg":"妥善率一直唔好<br />\n<br />\n佢地後勤係好有問題"},{"pid":"69ad98242ce8e36d12992aa51e864c7467dcc9e5","tid":2111132,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sad"},{"pid":"1856f1c128eb7b0ed0872f1eca11f76e548ff6c9","tid":2111132,"uid":296705,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f400ff10bcb060ac8317f00b15f369909ebe0847","tid":2111132,"uid":30274,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:38:06.000Z","msg":"台灣D軍隊硬係比人一種業餘既感覺...."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:51:12.000Z","msg":"😔😔<br />\n中共D軍隊硬係比人一種 淨係識摺被既感覺..."},{"pid":"a3a9a91c4c339f3dd0733201c3dc24145d86826d","tid":2111132,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T11:07:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200716/1762399.htm#ixzz6SLiFkCw5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200716%2F1762399.htm%23ixzz6SLiFkCw5&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=354f4ec2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200716/1762399.htm#ixzz6SLiFkCw5</a><br />\n<br />\n佢地就話係為左避下面民居先唔立即迫降"},{"pid":"2f0599b80009696e266ff3f6b496a0869e289a30","tid":2111132,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">台灣軍演直升機墜毀正副機師殉職 疑引擎轉速過慢</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538162-20200716.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538162-20200716.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=9b936dbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538162-20200716.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=05b3184e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538162-20200716.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n在台灣，一架參與漢光演習的軍方直升機意外墜毀，正副機師殉職。<br />\n<br />\n軍方表示，涉事的OH-58D戰搜直升機，演習後返回新竹空軍基地，大約下午3時30分，準備起飛回到龍潭基地，但在起飛不久硬著陸及起火。<br />\n<br />\n軍方初步懷疑直升機起飛後引擎轉速過慢，機師採取標準迫降程序，但最終墜毀，兩人送院搶救，其後不治。軍方成立專案小組調查原因，要求同款直升機停飛。台灣傳媒報道，同機型直升機已在兩年內，第三度發生意外。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文總統在社交網站發文表示哀悼，已經指示當局全力協助殉職官兵的家屬，並期望軍方繼續堅守崗位。"},{"pid":"c35ffc41d9e561b754866d686fc076f566bb2405","tid":2111132,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"1856f1c128eb7b0ed0872f1eca11f76e548ff6c9","t